","u": "Yes."},    {"who": "Wolf Nehrich", "start": "3680.538","u": "[reads] &#34;And the blood is hot and the girl so far, and the wind sings softly, and I like her so much. Oh, if faithful, if faithful she would stay to me. And the stones are hard but, hard but strong, and the walk, and we carry pickaxes and spades with us. And in the heart, in the heart, the love. Oh, Buchenwald, I cannot forget you, because you are my destiny. Only those, who leave you can imagine how wonderful freedom is. But Buchenwald, we won&#39;t moan and lament, and whatever our future may be. We want to say yes to life nevertheless, because one time the day will come and we&#39;ll be free, free, free.&#34;"},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "3712.503","u": "Yes. And this they allowed to be sung?"},    {"who": "Wolf Nehrich", "start": "3714.413","u": "Yes. We even had to sing it."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "3715.961","u": "You had to."},    {"who": "Wolf Nehrich", "start": "3716.485","u": "When sometimes you didn&#39;t have the head for it, you had to sing it."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "3719.196","u": "Yes, Now tell me . . ."},    {"who": "Wolf Nehrich", "start": "3721.497","u": "This is the Buchenwald emblem."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "3722.190","u": "Yes. This is supposed to be the Buchenwald sign? Triangle, was it Jewish or political?"},    {"who": "Wolf Nehrich", "start": "3726.841","u": "Political."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "3727.696","u": "I see. And the Jews had the political [unintelligible word]."},    {"who": "Wolf Nehrich", "start": "3730.136","u": "Yes. Political and additionally on top a yellow. That was [unintelligible word]."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "3732.847","u": "Ah, above were yellow signs. Now tell me this: Eh, how, Eh,eh: What are you planning to do now?"},    {"who": "Wolf Nehrich", "start": "3746.943","u": "Now, eh, I&#39;m in the vocational school of the ORT, I&#39;m learning carpentry. The vocational sc