you didn&#39;t have?"},    {"who": "Wolf Nehrich", "start": "3824.422","u": "No, not that."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "3825.356","u": "Did you have a prayer book?"},    {"who": "Wolf Nehrich", "start": "3828.169","u": "Maybe somebody could have it sown, sown in, and could then have hidden it somewhere in the camp."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "3833.169","u": "I see. So, what, how did you pray?"},    {"who": "Wolf Nehrich", "start": "3835.067","u": "By heart. However you could."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "3836.645","u": "I see. And, eh, did many know the Jewish prayers by heart? Did you know some?"},    {"who": "Wolf Nehrich", "start": "3843.362","u": "[speaks over Boder] Those who knew, knew. Not everybody, not always did you pray. Sometimes, you recited the [unintelligible word] by heart, or sometimes the [unintelligible word, both probably Jewish prayers] and that was already something."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "3852.940","u": "I see. And why did you say, that eh things, eh, ok, Well, eh, so now you&#39;re planning to go to Palestine?"},    {"who": "Wolf Nehrich", "start": "3864.202","u": "Yes."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "3864.575","u": "And your brother wants to go to Palestine."},    {"who": "Wolf Nehrich", "start": "3866.021","u": "Yes. Together with the brother."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "3867.106","u": "How do you think, how will you get there?"},    {"who": "Wolf Nehrich", "start": "3869.829","u": "Why. What, how, whatever possibility there is, that is how we&#39;ll go there."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "3876.136","u": "Well, this was very good Mr., eh, Nehrich. I am really glad I came over. And I think everything will be ok. And if I see the Rabbi Sch&#195;chter I will send him greetings."},    {"who": "Wolf Nehrich", "start": "3888.136","u": "Yes. Great pleasure."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "3892.203","u": "[In English] This concludes the interview with Wolf Nehrich, eh, in Geneva, at, eh, August the 26th 1946. We curtail, that we finish that at, eh, the spool of 25 minutes. He has spoken one full spool and 25 minutes on the other. And that is about all. Eh, Illinois Institute of Technology recording."}        ]
    }
_jsready = true;
var return_val;
switch (String(type)){
        case "transcription":
        return_val = transcription.interview;
        break;
            case "english_translation":
        return_val = english_translation.interview;
        break;
    }
return return_val;
}
function js_ready(){
    return _jsready;
}
