                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">K&#195;nigsh&#195;tte. Alright. This sounds English. K&#195;nigsh&#195;tte.</p>
                                                                                                <b>Wolf Nehrich</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Yes.</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Now tell me, eh: How were, how old were your brothers and sisters?</p>
                                                                                                <b>Wolf Nehrich</b>
                    <p class="utterance">The younger brother is born in 1930, and the older brother in 1924.</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">I see. And, eh, your sister?</p>
                                                                                                <b>Wolf Nehrich</b>
                    <p class="utterance">I didn&#39;t have one.</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">I see, so it was only two brothers.</p>
                                                                                                <b>Wolf Nehrich</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Yes</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
